data.meta_description: Santhosh Masilamani: I'm using Intch networking app to connect with new people. Contact me via Intch
data.text:
About myself

With over 8 years of experience in tech, DEI, and end to end recruitment across various industries, I have proven record of success. My achievements include an impressive number of filled critical positions, innovative sourcing strategies leading to improved candidate quality, reduced time-to-fill metrics, and enhanced diversity in hiring. I have also implemented a streamlined onboarding process. My accomplishments are marked by specific, quantifiable results and improvements, illustrating my commitment and proficiency in the field.

Job Description

I'm seeking a position in a collaborative work environment that offers challenging projects. I value a strong company culture and a firm that appreciates the importance of professional development. I'm eager to work in a company that aligns with my personal and professional values, reflecting a mutual understanding and respect.

How to contact

If you're interested, please fill the form. P.S. If you know a right person, please make an intro or share with him/her the link to this page.
